			<title><![CDATA[Nebius buys US AI inference startup Eigen AI in $643M deal]]></title>
			<category><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence]]></category>
			<link>https://tech.eu/2026/05/01/nebius-announces-construction-of-one-of-europes-largest-data-centres/</link>
