			<title><![CDATA[Berlin tech’s new reality: AI-driven output, stagnant wages, and a workforce on the move]]></title>
			<category><![CDATA[Data/Research]]></category>
			<link>https://tech.eu/2026/05/01/berlin-tech-s-new-reality-ai-driven-output-stagnant-wages-and-a-workforce-on-the-move/</link>
			<comments>https://tech.eu/2026/05/01/berlin-tech-s-new-reality-ai-driven-output-stagnant-wages-and-a-workforce-on-the-move/#comments</comments>
